iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager - Class in com.ihealth.communication.manager
Upgrade util class.
This is a singleton class, use iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager.getInstance() to get the instance. Use iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager.queryUpgradeInfoFromDeviceAndCloud(String, String) to get version info from device and cloud. Use iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager.isUpgradeState(String, String) to get the upgrade state of the device. Use iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager.startUpGrade(String, String) to start upgrade. Use iHealthDevicesUpgradeManager.stopUpgrade(String, String) to stop upgrade
